    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's kinda hard to have that balance if the \"accountability\" part is being used to label anything that disagrees with the mainstream narrative as \"harmful.\" if the goal is just to enforce one way of thinking by calling critics \"wrong\" or \"bigoted,\" isn't that basically just a way to shut down debate?",
